replies.author: Dragonsabremk3
replies.txt_content:
[09:51:58] [main/ERROR] [ToughAsNails Transformer]: Unexpected hash 902d050c7db38e549a3d4d207900f250 detected for class World. Crashes or bugs may occur!

看出来是ToughAsNails这个mod的问题，可以尝试更换更新的版本或者重新下载一次

 Expected stackmap frame at this location.
报的这个错误是java程序的事情，我百度的结果是你可以在启动参数添加这个 -XX:-UseSplitVerifier

一般不会在java这里出错，所以首先推荐从mod文件去解决
